  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Genjutsu, Visual, Auditory, unaware<br /><strong>Description</strong>: You whisper words of weakness, as the target becomes unable to put all its power into its attacks. Choose one creature you can see within range, it must make an intelligence saving throw:</p><ul><li><strong>Success</strong>: No effect</li><li><strong>Failure</strong>: For the duration, the target has all its damage reduced by half, and cannot ignore resistance nor ignore immunity or treat is as resistance. An affected creature repeat their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending this genjutsu on itself on a success.</li><li><strong>Critical Failure</strong>: As failure, but the target cannot repeat its saving throw.</li></ul><p><strong>At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank above B-rank, increase this jutsu's cost by +3, and the amount of creatures it can affect by +1.</p>",
